To run the unit all tests execute this command
phpunit --colors --verbose --bootstrap ../config/test_config.php .

To run individual tests 
phpunit --colors --verbose --bootstrap ../config/test_config.php <file>

Minimal Output 
phpunit --testdox --stop-on-failure --bootstrap ../config/test_config.php .

Generate HTML Docs
phpunit --coverage-html ./reports/ --bootstrap ../config/test_config.php .
